                          <note>Quire descriptions: quires 1–4 balanced; quires 5–6 unbalanced. Navigation system: white yarn is sewn into the fore edge of <locus target="#24 #25 #26" facs="025 025 026">fols. 24, 25, 26</locus> to mark content.</note>
                          <list>
                              <item xml:id="q1" n="1">
                                 <dim unit="leaf">2</dim>
